@startuml REQ-0103_Error_Reporting
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "User" as User
entity "Mobile" as Mobile
entity "MCU" as MCU
entity "Cloud" as Cloud

box "IoT Library" #LightBlue
  participant "IoT Library" as IoT_Library
end box

header
  **REQ-0103: Error Reporting**
  //Description:// Forward MCU error notifications to cloud for remote\ndiagnostics and alerting.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Error info published to device/error topic.
end header


MCU --> IoT_Library: error_report
== on_error_report() ==
IoT_Library -> Cloud: MQTT: device/error

@enduml